OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774033869
OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,FRestoration work on the historic
OL,7,FBirnbeck Pier in Weston-super-Mare can
OL,8,Fnow be finished after the government
OL,9,Fpledged a further #19 million towards
OL,10,Fthe project.
OL,12,FIt brings the total spend on restoring
OL,13,Fwhat has become an eyesore to #44
OL,14,Fmillion.
OL,16,FThe government cash will come from the
OL,17,FGrowth Mission Fund, it will help
OL,18,Frestore the clock tower, turnstiles,
OL,19,Frepair the boathouse, renovate the
OL,20,Fpavilion buildings and restore the
OL,21,FNorth Jetty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
