OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774033869
OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,FIn its heyday the pier was the
OL,7,FVictorian and then Edwardian
OL,8,Fequivalent of a modern theme-park. It
OL,9,Fclosed 30 years ago because of safety
OL,10,Fworries.
OL,12,FAnnouncing the extra cash Chancellor
OL,13,FRachel Reeves said: "The restoration
OL,14,Fof the iconic Birnbeck Pier will make
OL,15,Fthe area a more attractive place to
OL,16,Flive, work, visit and start a business
OL,17,Fin the years to come."
OL,26,@uD@UOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
