FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774033869
OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,FNeil O'Donoghue, the Business Director
OL,7,Fof the Birnbeck Regeneration Trust,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are absolutely delighted
OL,9,Fwith this wonderful news.
OL,11,F"For the Government to release such
OL,12,Fsignificant funding for Birnbeck Pier,
OL,13,Fan important piece of local history
OL,14,Fheld so dearly by so many people in
OL,15,FWeston and far beyond, is truly
OL,16,Fremarkable."
OL,18,FAfter years of setbacks and
OL,19,Funcertainty the first major works to
OL,20,Frestore the Grade II* pier started in
OL,21,FFebruary.
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
