OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,FA 100-tonne crane started work on the
OL,7,Flandmark which is the only pier in the
OL,8,FUK to connect to an island.
OL,10,FWhat is left of the fragile pier will
OL,11,Fbe reconstructed, and its cast-iron
OL,12,Flegs will be the only element of the
OL,13,Foriginal structure which remains.
OL,15,FCouncillor Mike Bell, Leader of North
OL,16,FSomerset Council, said: "#19m is a
OL,17,Fgame-changing amount of money. I can't
OL,18,Funderestimate what today's
OL,19,Fannouncement means.
OL,26,@xD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
