PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774033869
OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,F"Not only is it great news for our
OL,7,Fproject to restore Birnbeck Pier but
OL,8,Fthis will boost growth and create a
OL,9,Fmore prosperous future for local
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"The additional funding will enable us
OL,13,Fto carry out work to buildings on the
OL,14,Flandside and island and we hope will
OL,15,Falso fulfil our ambition to restore
OL,16,Fthe north jetty.
OL,18,F"This will bring the Grade II* Listed
OL,19,Fpier site fully back to life as a
OL,20,Fheritage and visitor attraction of
OL,21,Fsignificant national importance."
OL,26,@tD@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
