CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774033869
OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,FDan Aldridge MP said: "Securing this
OL,7,Fmoney means we can now move forward
OL,8,Fwith the full restoration of one of
OL,9,Fthe most remarkable landmarks in the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,F"But this project has always been
OL,13,Fabout more than simply restoring a
OL,14,Fpier. My focus is making sure Birnbeck
OL,15,FPier becomes sustainable for the long
OL,16,Fterm, a place that serves our
OL,17,Fcommunity as well as tourists.
OL,26,@nD@WOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
