OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774033869
OL,3,CRestoration of historic Birnbeck Pier
OL,4,Cgets extra #19 million funding
OL,6,F"That means creating spaces for
OL,7,Fexhibitions, training, local events,
OL,8,Fhospitality, and community activity so
OL,9,Fthe pier can be alive all year round,
OL,10,Fnot just in the summer months.
OL,12,F"Birnbeck should be a hub for Weston,
OL,13,Fsomewhere people come together, where
OL,14,Fopportunities are created and where
OL,15,Fthe whole town can feel proud again."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@eO]
